high_descs: Turn left, walk to end of counter, turn right, walk to wall
Pick up plunger off of floor
Open cupboard below sink, place plunger inside, close cupboard
anns.task_desc: Move plunger from beside the toilet to under the counter

high_descs: Turn to the left and then the right to face the toilet paper.
Pick up the plunger from the left of the toilet.
Carry the plunger and turn around. Then turn left and right to face the sink.
Open the bottom right cabinet and place the plunger inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a plunger to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward just past the counter, then turn right and walk to the plunger on the floor.
Pick up the plunger from the floor.
Turn around and walk forward to the cabinets below the sink on the right.
Put the plunger in the bottom right cabinet, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Move a plunger from the floor to a cabinet.
